metadata.name: Poke NFT
metadata.description: PokeNFTs is a collection of 4,888 nfts representing the first 151 pokemon of the first generation.(KANTO)The collection is made up of 32 pieces per pokemon including two shiny. There are also 56 secret golden cards.The collection aims to offer benefits to its holders such as access to other free mint, gifts such as consoles, plush, posters, goodies, pokemon PSA cards in the form of contests for NFT holders.All representations of first generation pokemon are fan art and in no way represent the intellectual property of Game Freak or the pokemon company.
